      <title>米莱开始削减阿根廷低收入人群的能源补贴</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/milei-begins-to-slash-energy-subsidies-for-low-income-argentines</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着总统哈维尔·米莱推行经济休克疗法，大多数阿根廷家庭本月的电费将大幅上涨，他们将面临一个格外严酷的冬季。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/milei-begins-to-slash-energy-subsidies-for-low-income-argentines</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 14:35:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
